	(text "SEC A  CONTROLLER (mains-side domain, DGND): Teensy 4.1 + TFT/touch + buttons. Ethernet = PJRC Ethernet Kit on Teensy bottom pads. Floating +5VD arrives from linear PSU at J6."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30 25 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "7f955b6f-c468-4a8c-bfe5-7bbb13c17a4c")
	)
	(text "SEC B  ISOLATION BARRIER: U2 SPI+control, U3/U4 relay coils + ADC readback. Left of chips = DGND/+3V3 domain, right = STAR/+5VD floating domain. Keep >=6mm creepage under U2-U4."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30 122 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "81fa77ff-2119-421d-badb-7f216b59716a")
	)
	(text "ADC + reference moved to the FE board (rev C) - VOUT never leaves that PCB. J4 (20-pin) carries the four ADC lines through the isolators."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30 222 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "2a7fd37d-ca05-42ee-8121-7babecb42bf3")
	)
	(text "NOTES: (1) VERIFY LTC2500 filter config word + SPI timing at bring-up (firmware adc_ltc2500.cpp TODO). (2) TBD62083 = DMOS ULN2803 replacement, same pinout."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30 340 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "207bd461-3688-4f22-aff4-f7576dde1a45")
	)
	(text "(3) Floating-domain logic is 5V; Teensy side 3.3V via isolators. (4) Analog +/-12V goes to FE J2 only; STAR commons join at the FE board."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30 345 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "87f0b57b-1e8a-4165-a3fe-f036baa346a9")
	)
	(text "(5) U4 spare fwd channels C/D tied low."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30 350 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "d584a656-794f-4026-b456-7c3c7e25a3f3")
	)
